      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "I hear the crushing weight of your peers moving ahead while you feel stranded in a void, and it makes sense why you see no path forward when your foundation has been removed. You are right that there is nothing tangible to move toward right now, but this hollow feeling is often just the mind trying to convince you that your worth is tied to a single outcome that never happened. Please consider that this void is not a permanent state of being, but a temporary space where you can finally rest without the pressure of climbing.",
      "source": "target",
